  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张Governance Action（GA）的完整生命周期流程图，从任何人提交提案开始，到最终生效或者失败。核心是要体现DReps、SPOs和宪法委员会这三个投票主体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是一个提交节点，然后进入投票阶段。这三个主体是并行投票吗？还是按顺序？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "并行的。DReps用委托的ada投票，SPOs用质押权重，宪法委员会专门检查合宪性。三者独立投票，然后汇总到批准环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我设计一个子图B叫\"Voting phase\"，里面三个节点横向排列，分别标注这三类投票者。然后统一流向Ratification节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但Ratification节点要说明清楚：根据GA类型不同，可能需要2个或3个机构批准。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Ratification节点，标注\"GA approved by 2 or 3 bodies depending on the type\"。接下来批准之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "批准后进入Enactment，记录上链，然后在下一个epoch边界生效。另外还需要一个失败分支：如果没批准，押金在流程结束后返还。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "X"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Enactment和Effective是两个节点吗？还是合并？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "建议分开：D是\"Enactment\"（记录上链），E是\"Effective at next epoch boundary\"。这样逻辑更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
